To create docker container to run the project in an development environment
  docker run --rm -it --mount type=bind,source=$(pwd)/,target=/app -p 3000:3000 node:20.15.1 bash
    After running the command above, run the following commands inside the container
      cd /app
      npm install
      npm start

Using container you don't need to install nodejs in your machine, just docker

