⇒  npx create-next-app@latest

⇒  npx create-next-app
    command to create app next.js

⇒  npx create-react-app {name} --template redux-typescript
    command to create react app using redux with typscript

⇒ npm install @mui/x-data-grid
    command to install material ui data grid

⇒ npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled
    command to install material ui

⇒ npm install @fontsource/roboto
    command to install roboto font
    or add this link in index.html
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,500,700&display=swap" />

⇒ npm install @mui/icons-material
    command to install material ui icons
    or add this link in index.html
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Material+Icons" />

⇒ npm install react-router@6 react-router-dom@6
    command to install react router v6

⇒ npm install @mui/x-data-grid
    command to install material ui data grid

⇒ npm install notistack
    command to install notistack


React testing library
⇒ npm install --save-dev @testing-library/react @testing-library/jest-dom
    command to install react testing library

⇒ npm i msw@0.49.3 --save-dev
    command to install msw

=> npm i keycloak-js
    command to install keycloak-js

